      "name": "Mesh independence study — discretization error assessment",
      "description": "Three-level mesh refinement study (coarse 2.1M, medium 4.8M, fine 9.6M cells) on the FDA centrifugal pump geometry. Grid convergence index (GCI) computed for shear stress and velocity profiles at all five operating points. Maximum GCI of 3.2% confirms discretization error within acceptable bounds for MRL 2.",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/evidence/mesh-independence-study-report-2024"
