    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model adequately predicts hemolysis index with mean absolute error of 8.4% against FDA pump experimental data. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1.0 confirmed at all five operating points. The credibility assessment supports use of the CFD model to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device in the 510(k) regulatory decision context.",
